@startuml agenticWorkflow-state
hide empty description

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Running : run()
Idle --> ConfiguringSteps : addStep()

ConfiguringSteps --> ConfiguringSteps : addStep()
ConfiguringSteps --> Running : run()

Running --> ExecutingStep : next step
ExecutingStep --> ExecutingStep : step completes\n(if more steps)
ExecutingStep --> Completed : all steps done
ExecutingStep --> ErrorState : exception caught

ErrorState --> Idle : error logged
Completed --> Idle : reset

note right of ConfiguringSteps
  Agent can only run
  if steps exist
end note

note right of ExecutingStep
  WorkflowFormatException
  is caught and logged
end note
@enduml